ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisOrder amending P.C. 2013-909, which appoints individuals to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO, by (1) extending the Hon. Heather J. Smith's appointment from January 5, 2014 to January 10, 2014 inclusive; (2) appointing the Hon. Kathryn N. Feldman from January 11 to 30, 2014 inclusive; and (3) appointing the Hon. Robert J. Sharpe effective January 31, 2014.
